places.name: Jumma Masjid Guduvancheri

featured_reviews.review_id:
Renovated and reopened on 27/11/2022.

Very close to GST Road and nearer to Guduvanchery Railway Station

Spacious masjid and good air flow.

Prayer on the 1st floor with a capacity of 500 people at a time.

Provision for Lift is underway.

Madrasa on the ground floor.

Parking space is very limited.

Enough space for ablution, limited on washroom.
